 {[#]} {How to continue here?} 10... d4 $1 {We are happy to open up the center.}
11. exd4 exd4 12. Qxd4 (12. Nxd4 Qb6 $1 {[%cal Gf8d8] The position is very
risky for White.} 13. a3 {The only move which keeps the balance.} (13. Nf3 Rd8
14. Qc2 g5 15. Bg3 Nc6 $17 {[%cal Gg5g4,Gc6d4] 0-1 (35) Edouard,R (2613)
-Nakamura,H (2785) Caleta 2017 CBM 177 [Navara,D]}) 13... Rd8 14. Bxf6 Qxf6 15.
axb4 Rxd4 16. Qe2 Be6 $36 {The position remains unpleasant for White and we
will win the pawn on c$ soon>}) 12... g5 13. Bg3 (13. Qxd8 Rxd8 14. Bg3 Ne4 15.
Be2 Re8 $11 {[%cal Re8e1]}) 13... Nc6 {We are happy to go into the endgame
with our active pieces despite being a pawn down.} 14. Qxd8 Rxd8 15. Be2 Ne4
16. O-O Bxc3 17. bxc3 Be6 $44 {We have full compensation for the pawn and are
likely to win the pawn on c4 shortly.} *

