 {[#]} {How to continue here?} 10... e4 $1 {We need to stop White from going e4
and f4 is not as good as it was with the bishop g3.} 11. f4 (11. Ne2 Nbd7 12.
Ng3 exf3 13. gxf3 Ne5 14. Be2 Bh3 $17 {We will castle long next.}) 11... Nbd7 {
We are not in a hurry. We can bring the knight to the kingside via f8.} 12. Nh3
(12. Ne2 Ng4 13. Bg1 f5 $17) 12... g4 13. Ng1 Nf8 14. Bh4 Ng6 $17 *

